    "description": "&quot;Stay awhile, and face me&quot;<br><br><strong>Shufflepoker</strong> is a revisited poker game with current auto-battlers rules like Teamfight Tactics or Hearthstone Battlegrounds.<br>In a welcoming tavern, face others adventurers who are looking for fame, with diverse skills and behaviors.<br>Be warned : they will not let you win without hardly fight!<br>Draw your cards and place them on your board, then make combinations to defeat your challenger.<br>Discover a new version of Poker: first, choose your special power carefully, it could change everything !<br><br>Start the game : draw five cards and select the ones that you want to buy to make your board, then create your combination and face the one of<br>your enemy. Stronger is your combination, the more damages you will inflict at the end of the turn.<br>During the next turn, choose cards which will join your board and complete those which were unused from the last turn.<br>The game is over when one of the players has no point left.<br><br>Choose your game mode :<br>- in solo mode: challenge one of the tavern’s regular and face up to 8 adversaries with different behaviors to train yourself.<br>- in online mode: face another random player with limited time for each turn (warning : limited number of places)",
